Hook nodded. "It is comming along nicely, and will give us the speed we
need," he then turned disgustedly at Scavanger, "If we could ever find
our hyper drive." he said impatiently.
______________________________________________________
Spinister silently moved aside, to show Needlenose, he then bowed.
